Program Name:
------------

   "ULTIMATE GIN"

   GIN.EXE

Equipment:
----------

   REQUIRED:
       1. IBM Compatible Computer
       2. EGA/VGA with 256K on card
       3. Hard disk
       4. 550K free RAM
   OPTIONAL:
       1. Mouse
       2. Disk caching software
       3. 286 or better processor
       4. Sound Blaster

Description:
-----------

Short:

   Go where no GIN player has gone before -- into the Ultimate Zone.
   Enter a fully animated GIN RUMMY game.  Play with 1 of 4 notorious
   computer characters in one of the toughest games you've ever had.
   Select the game variation you want to play.  Hollywood scoring if
   desired.  Set the game game and bonus points, challenge a player to
   to a new match or play up to 40 games per match.  Much more.  You
   won't want to stop playing this game.

Long:

   Go where no GIN player has gone before -- into the Ultimate Zone.
   Enter a fully animated GIN RUMMY game.  Play with 1 of 4 notorious
   computer characters in one of the toughest games you've ever had.
   Select the game variation you want to play.  Hollywood scoring if
   desired.  Set the game game and bonus points, challenge a player to
   to a new match or play up to 40 games per match.  Control the game
   speed, review the score book at any time.  Make your opponent keep
   quiet.  Much more.

